 : 1px;" src="en\imgspec\CouleursStd1.png"> <span class="rvts7">or</span> <img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle; padding : 1px;" src="en\imgspec\CouleursRal1.png"> <span class="rvts7">.</span> </p><p class="rvps3"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en\imgspec\SelectCouleurs.png"></p><p class="rvps3"> <span class="rvts7">The value can also be entered manually. It is a mixture of 3 numbers (each ranging from 0 to 255) corresponding to the three colors Red-Green-Blue (RGB), for example a magenta value will be <span class="rvts18"><span class="rvts7">&quot;213,43,183&quot;</span></span></span> </p><p class="rvps3"> <span class="rvts7">The operation affects the color (red) to the added layer.</span> </p><p class="rvps3"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en\imgspec\Oper-piece30.png"><span class="rvts7"> &#xA0;</span><img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle; padding : 1px;" src="en\imgspec\CouleursStd.png"></p><p class="rvps3"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en\imgspec\CouleursRal.png"></p><p class="rvps3"> <span class="rvts7"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps3"> <span class="rvts7"><br></span> </p><p></p></div><div id="topic_footer"><div id="topic_footer_content"> Copyright Â© 2017 by Visiativ. All Rights Reserved. </div></div>